      FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
      "84666130-ff93-4ead-8021-1aa50d4ca620"],
     "\[LineSeparator]returns a new basis of the subspace ",
     Cell[BoxData[
      RowBox[{
       SubscriptBox["\[ScriptCapitalW]", "\[UpTee]"], "\[Subset]", 
