      FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
      "0a00ce86-b349-4fb5-ba26-8164a3585adc"],
     "  that is orthogonal to ",
     Cell[BoxData[
      RowBox[{"\[ScriptCapitalW]", "\[Subset]", "\[ScriptCapitalV]"}]], 
      "InlineFormula",
      FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
      "1bbbfd9f-bbb1-4e06-898a-e8bceb65da97"],
     ", where \[ScriptCapitalV] is the vector space spanned by the basis ",
     Cell[BoxData[
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{
        SubscriptBox[
         StyleBox["v", "TI"], 
         StyleBox["1", "TR"]], ",", 
        SubscriptBox[
