      FontFamily->"Source Sans Pro",ExpressionUUID->
      "6fe5f518-988c-4358-a3a6-ac5e73492b4d"],
     ", and \[ScriptCapitalW] is the subspace of \[ScriptCapitalV] spanned by \
the basis ",
     Cell[BoxData[
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{
        SubscriptBox[
         StyleBox["w", "TI"], 
